-- Manchester Utd. Targets PSV Midfielder Strootman, Mirror Reports
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-04-01T11:49:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/manchester-utd-targets-psv-midfielder-strootman-mirror-reports.html
Manchester United is ready to sign
PSV Eindhoven midfielder Kevin Strootman for 15 million pounds
($24 million), the Sunday Mirror reported.    United has watched Strootman 12 times in recent weeks and
believes a deal is close to being completed,  the newspaper said ,
citing sources at the Premier League soccer club it didn’t name.  The 22-year-old has played in 10 of the Dutch national
team’s past 11 matches and is expected to be a key part of the
squad at this year’s European Championship, the Mirror said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  